0edf5607-74ae-461d-bc5c-229b5d5dae1c.description:
Receives up to 10 records to be updated in AirTable.

Example:
```json
[
  {
    "id": "rect1iBB9su0rT0JI",
    "fields": {
      "number column": 0,
      "string column": "value0"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "recpIPBXdPlv5wv7D",
    "fields": {
      "number column": 1,
      "string column": "value1",
      "bool column": true
    }
  }
]
```

03e1931c-8be9-4518-948a-54d2314cfc36.description:
Sends the records that were successfully updated in AirTable.

Example:
```json
[
  {
    "number column": 0,
    "string column": "value0"
  },
  {
    "number column": 1,
    "string column": "value1",
    "bool column": true
  }
]
```

43783563-c3ec-426c-bed1-481528e08d45.description:
Sends records that were successfully updated in AirTable, in the format returned by AirTable, including metadata like row ID.

Example:
```json
[
  {
    "id": "rect1iBB9su0rT0JI",
    "createdTime": "2022-09-29T07:25:20.000Z",
    "fields": {
      "number column": 0,
      "string column": "value0"
    }
  },
  {
    "id": "recpIPBXdPlv5wv7D",
    "createdTime": "2022-09-29T07:25:20.000Z",
    "fields": {
      "number column": 1,
      "string column": "value1",
      "bool column": true
    }
  }
]
```
